reviews.text:
Great place to enjoy the evening with your loved ones. Service is great & the food is always delicious!! Very fresh!
Our pokey sticks- add mushrooms & sausage!

Pretty decent pizza for a fairly reasonable price. I ordered the extra cheese, extra pepperoni, etc. I was expecting more for being ‚Äúextra,‚Äù but it‚Äôs fair everything considered. Gets extra Star for keeping ‚ÄúGumby‚Äù alive from my childhood. Super greasy, but I sometimes dig greasy.

It was a fun atmosphere and the pizza was tasty - will come again - but next time I‚Äôll try blockhead. Got the chicken bacon ranch with a light jalape√±o and dipped in jalape√±o ranch with a stoner pie pizza ( French fries and morels sticks on top - don‚Äôt knock it till ya try it! ) Everyone with us enjoyed their food.. took awhile to serve us but we had a big party. TRY IT ! We were glad we did !

Good experience overall. If you just order pizza rolls, they have those ready almost instantly, but wings will take a while. The wings were large & flavors were good. Only complaint is that the edges of my flatbread were burnt so I was only able to eat part of it. The pepperoni pizza rolls are best with a sauce (ranch and/or garlic butter are my favorites)!

Love me some Gumby‚Äôs! Went in as I was leaving town. Midday, not too crowded, food was fresh and the quality was great. Service was the best I‚Äôve had in a long while. Games on every TV and cool music playing to boot‚Ä¶. Highly recommend for quality pizza at a decent price.

editorial_summary.overview: Informal chain offering an extensive menu of pizza, wings & Italian comfort food.
